{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wens felka Glihtums\nDahwida/ preeſch ta\naugſta Dseedataja/ par\nBamahzifchannu no tahs Leezi-\nas Rohſes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad wiꞥſch kawahs ar\neem Sihrereem no Mesopota-\nnijas/ un ar teem Sihrereem\no Jobas/ un Joabs atpakkat\nahze/ un no teem Eedomiteeem\niwiipadehnits tuhſtoſchus kawe\nSahts-Eeleija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Deews/ kas tu muhs at-\netttis/ iſkaitijs un duſmigs bi-\ns/ greesees atkaſ pee muhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas tu to Semmi kuſti-\najs/ un ſchehlis eſti/ dseedina\nvinnas Plihfumus/ jo wixxa\nchaubahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſti taweeim Laudim\nruhtn Leetu lizzis redſeht/ tu\nfi muhs ar Breefinibas Wih-\nu dsirdinajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "(Tatschu) tu eſti teem/\nas tevis bihſtahs weenu Karro-\nu dewis/ ka tee to uſzeltu tahs\nBateefibas labbad/ Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ka tawi Mihkee\naptu atfwabbinati/ tad palih-\nsi nu ar tawn labbu Rohku/ un\naklaust muhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Deews runna tawa ſweh-\na Weeta/ pahr to es preeza-\nobs/ es dallischu Sikenii/ un\nnehroſcht to Eeleiju Sukot.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gileads man peederr/ tr\nManaffus man peederr/ un Ee-\nvrains irr mannas Galwas\nStiprums/ Juhda irr mans\nWaldons,\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Moabs irr mans masga-\njamajs Bohds/ mannu Kurpi\nſteepju es pahr Eedomu/ ta\nWilisteru Semme gawile man\npretti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas waddihs mann wee-\nnâ stipra Pilsfahta? kas pawad-\ndihs mann lihds Eedomain?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi tu Deews/ kas tu\nmuhs effi atinettis/ un ne iglah-\nji ak Deews! ar muhsu Karra-\nSpehku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eedohd mums Paligu\nBehdu Laika/ jo Zilweku Peſti-\nſchana irr nederriga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ar Deewa darriſtim mehs\nſtiprus Darbus/ tas patsmuh-\ntu Prettimekus faspahtdihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta LXI. Dseesma.\nJrr weena luhsmana Dseesma/ eefch ka tohp\nmahzihts/ ka teem Patwalſfneefeem preeſch\nſaweem Walditajeem buhs Deewu luht-\nWarr arridsan no Dahwida faprasfa tapt/\nkas Deewu peefaun/ ka tas winnu iglahhji:\n2. Jo wiꞥſch eſtu leelaks Behdas: 3. Un\nDeews eſtu winnu arridsan lihdsſchim no\ndauds Behdahm ispestijs: 4. Tapehzzerre\nwiꞥſch/ ka Deews arri ſcho Reisi winnam\npalihdsehs: 5. Tad grihbub wiꞥſch jawu\nApfohlichannu nomakſaht: 9.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wena Dahwida Dseef-\nma/ preeſch ta augſta\nDseedataja us Negi-\nnot.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klansi ak Deews! mannu\nSaufschannu/ xenun wehra man-\nnu Luhgſchannu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Semmes Galla pee-\nfauzu es teuis/ kad manna\nSirde behdajahs/waddi tu man-\nnes weenu itt * augſtu Amira-\nRatnu.\n"
    }
  ],
